column2: Election Commission of Malaysia (SPR), Tindak Malaysia (2024), YB Syahredzan Johan

The results are derived from the YB Syahredzan Johan X Post (https://x.com/syahredzan/status/1840004877143159288). Limited validation was performed. The focus is only on the ordinary vote, not early vote and postal vote data. Total votes for BN is 27995 and PN is 7347. Unofficial data has undercounted BN by 54 votes and PN by 25 votes.
